---
// CTAFinal.astro — CTA final da LP My Library
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-amber-950 to-rose-950 ml-section relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative books silhouettes -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/4 flex gap-1 items-end">
      {['h-32 bg-amber-400', 'h-24 bg-rose-400', 'h-40 bg-teal-400', 'h-28 bg-purple-400', 'h-36 bg-orange-400'].map(c => (
        <div class={`w-8 ${c} rounded-t-sm`}></div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 flex gap-1 items-end">
      {['h-20 bg-blue-400', 'h-44 bg-amber-500', 'h-28 bg-green-400', 'h-36 bg-rose-500', 'h-24 bg-indigo-400'].map(c => (
        <div class={`w-8 ${c} rounded-t-sm`}></div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-8">
    <div class="ml-reveal space-y-5">
      <span class="text-5xl">📚</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
        Sua estante está esperando.<br/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-rose-400">
          Comece a construir sua biblioteca hoje.
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Cada livro que você folheou, cada história que te transformou — eles merecem um lugar bonito para existir.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="ml-reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="https://app.mylibrary.com.br"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-rose-500 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-amber-500/30 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 text-lg"
      >
        📖 Adicionar meu primeiro livro
      </a>
      <a
        href="#precos"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/30 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-200 text-lg"
      >
        Experimentar grátis
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="ml-reveal text-white/50 text-sm">
      Gratuito para começar · Sem cartão de crédito · Cancele quando quiser
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
